data.description: ** MOTIVATED SELLER BRING ALL OFFERS!!!! Beautiful property WILL NOT LAST!** A beautiful home with 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and a bonus room that can serve various purposes. The master bedroom features a jacuzzi bathtub for added luxury. All rooms are generously sized, with enough space to fit king-sized beds, and still have room for other furniture. The cozy fireplace in one of the rooms adds warmth and charm to the living space. The kitchen is spacious and well-equipped with ample cabinets and barn doors, making it an ideal place for cooking and entertaining. The home has a split plan with an office, a family room, and a separate office/den with a fireplace. The property sits on a 1-acre lot with a chain-link fenced backyard that also includes an RV outlet 50 AMP. There is also a screened-in porch, 2 sheds, and a pole barn for additional storage and outdoor activities. The roof was replaced in 2018.
